  "description": "The 2025 Fat Boy ® Gray Ghost pays tribute to a legend that defined an era and captured the hearts of generations. Honoring the unmistakable style of the 1990 original, this Icon ensures the legacy lives on. Reimagined with more power and attitude, it’s back to make history again. In 1988 and 1989, Willie G. Davidson rode early Fat Boy ® prototypes into Daytona, seeking direct feedback from riders and igniting a legacy that would span generations. By 1990, the Fat Boy was born, quickly becoming one of the most legendary models in Harley-Davidson history. Now, 35 years later, the new 2025 Fat Boy ® Gray Ghost charges forward, bringing that legacy full circle.",
